+ * @uaddr1:     Address where waiters are currently waiting on
+ * @uaddr2:     New address to wait
+ * @nr_wake:    Number of waiters at uaddr1 to be wake
+ * @nr_requeue: After waking nr_wake, number of waiters to be requeued
